652
00:52:49,599 --> 00:52:52,920
I don't understand what you're saying.

653
00:52:53,960 --> 00:52:57,079
But I remember something
from when I was little.

654
00:52:58,719 --> 00:52:59,679
What is it?

655
00:53:01,960 --> 00:53:04,280
My father was bitten by a snake.

656
00:53:04,760 --> 00:53:07,800
My mother urged the doctor
to look for the herbs at night.

657
00:53:08,360 --> 00:53:12,480
Unexpectedly, the doctor
fell off the cliff and died.

658
00:53:13,559 --> 00:53:16,400
After that,
my mother always felt guilty.

659
00:53:16,599 --> 00:53:18,159
She got sick for many years.

660
00:53:19,079 --> 00:53:22,119
Should my mother be to blame?

661
00:53:22,679 --> 00:53:26,519
She shouldn't be, but not quite.

